idinfo.native: Microsoft Windows Vista Version 6.1 (Build 7601) Service Pack 1; ESRI ArcCatalog 9.3.1.3000

descript.purpose:
Merged polygons of all teams from 2009 to 2011 season in Kazanluk, included. Useful for mathematical measurments, operation and calculations ( Counts are all proper) Dates and Leader columns have been deleted by Arc in the process of merging, therefore are unusable. Not good for general overview, but good for density displays and arithmetic operations.
last edits: I completed missing attributes for LU / Vis in l team C 2009 ATS polygons on the basis of topo views • Check Charlotte’s diary for true data • Check artefact table that there are no diags found for these I filled in Visibility in Team B (21637 – 21646) survey units in GIS to 80-100%. This info is not explicitly filled in the pdf forms and would merit revisiting.
I reviewed polygons where Walker Interval was <10 and changed intensity to Urban (high intensity) or ATS - different categories applied in different contexts I reviewed LU, where null or odd (Communacation had replaced beach) and fixed. I reviewed polygons that had multiple nulls in the methodological variables.
What needs to be done: team leader and date of walking is needed in this shapefile
descript.supplinf: Contains pure polygon data, not suitable for site display (use detailed TeamsMerged or original team polygons)
